Package com.hexaware.controller

Class VehicleService

java.lang.Object
com.hexaware.controller.VehicleService
All Implemented Interfaces:
IVehicleService
public class VehicleService extends Object implements IVehicleService
Provides services related to vehicles such as retrieving available vehicles, updating vehicle details, adding new vehicles, removing vehicles, and fetching all vehicles.
